  "conformsToProfile": "https://uofa.net/vocab#ProfileMinimal",
  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Intended use is limited to Class II spinal fixation devices evaluated under ASTM F1717 quasi-static compression-bending loading in a simulated L4-L5 construct, supporting 510(k) substantial equivalence determination.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-structural-performance",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-experimental-n11-lab1",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-experimental-n11-lab2"
  ],
  "hasValidationResult": [
